				<div class="soft-card rounded-[1.75rem] p-6">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.045em] text-primary">Warning Signs a Schedule May Need Adjustment</h2>
					<p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-secondary">These signs do not automatically mean the schedule is wrong, but they may suggest parents should simplify transitions, review sleep routines, or adjust separation length.</p>
					<ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 text-sm leading-6 text-secondary">
